        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Your judgment has grown in divine power, instilling fear in those you condemn. Whenever you use your Judgment ability, you can spend 1 wrath, and if the target has [[potency P average]], they are frightened of you (save ends). Additionally, whenever a creature judged by you is reduced to 0 Hit Points and you use Judgment as a free triggered action, if the new target has [[potency P strong]], they are frightened of you (save ends). If the target is already frightened of you, they instead take {holy damage} equal to twice your Presence score.</p>",
